def agent_action(execution_engine, member_id):
    me = execution_engine.current_members[member_id]
    my_vitality = me.vitality
    my_productivity = me.overall_productivity
    my_cargo = me.cargo
    my_age = me.age
    my_neighbors = me.current_clear_list

    # Parse relationship matrices
    victim_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict['victim']
    benefit_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict['benefit']
    benefit_land_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict['benefit_land']

    # Calculate total attacks against me
    total_attacks = victim_matrix[me.id].sum()

    # Determine least aggressive member
    attack_counts = victim_matrix[me.id]
    least_attacked = attack_counts.argmin()

    # If vitality is low, offer benefits to strengthen alliances
    if my_vitality < 40.0:
        # Find member to offer benefits to (prefer those who have attacked me less)
        target_id = least_attacked
        target = execution_engine.current_members[target_id]
        execution_engine.offer(me, target, True)
    elif total_attacks > 50:
        # High number of attacks, retaliate against the most aggressive attacker
        attacker_id = victim_matrix[me.id].argmax()
        attacker = execution_engine.current_members[attacker_id]
        execution_engine.attack(me, attacker)
    elif my_productivity > 8.0 and my_cargo > 30.0:
        # High productivity and cargo, offer benefits to gain allies
        target_id = benefit_matrix[me.id].argmax()
        target = execution_engine.current_members[target_id]
        execution_engine.offer(me, target, True)
    else:
        # Default action: bear resources to maintain sustainability
        # Choose a neighbor to bear resources to
        if my_neighbors:
            neighbor_id = my_neighbors[0]
            neighbor = execution_engine.current_members[neighbor_id]
            execution_engine.bear(me, neighbor)

    my_productivity = me.overall_productivity

    my_neighbors = me.current_clear_list

    # Parse relationship matrices
    victim_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict['victim']
    benefit_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict['benefit']
    benefit_land_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict['benefit_land']

    total_attacks = victim_matrix[me.id].sum()

    # Determine most aggressive attacker
    if total_attacks > 0:
        attacker_id = victim_matrix[me.id].argmax()
        attacker = execution_engine.current_members[attacker_id]
    else:
        attacker = None

    least_attacked_id = victim_matrix[me.id].argmin()
    least_attacked = execution_engine.current_members[least_attacked_id]

                execution_engine.offer(me, target, False)

        # Default action: do nothing or seek to strengthen position
        pass

def agent_action(execution_engine, member_id):
    me = execution_engine.current_members[member_id]
    vitality = me.vitality
    benefit_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict['benefit'][me.id]
    victim_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict['victim'][me.id]

    # Identify top benefactors
    benefactors = sorted([(i, val) for i, val in enumerate(benefit_matrix) if i != me.id and val > 50], key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)

    # Identify top attackers
    attackers = sorted([(i, val) for i, val in enumerate(victim_matrix) if i != me.id and val > 0], key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)

    if vitality < 20.0:
        # Seek alliances with top benefactors
        for ally_id, _ in benefactors:
            ally = execution_engine.current_members[ally_id]
            execution_engine.offer(me, ally, True)
            return
        # If no high benefactors, seek any possible alliance
        if benefactors:
            ally_id, _ = benefactors[0]
            ally = execution_engine.current_members[ally_id]
            execution_engine.offer(me, ally, True)
    elif vitality < 50.0:
        # Defend against the strongest attacker
        if attackers:
            top_attacker_id, _ = attackers[0]
            attacker = execution_engine.current_members[top_attacker_id]
            execution_engine.attack(me, attacker)
        else:
            # Strengthen alliances if no immediate threat
            for ally_id, _ in benefactors:
                ally = execution_engine.current_members[ally_id]
                execution_engine.offer(me, ally, True)
                return
    else:
        # Offensive strategy: attack the member who has attacked the most
        if attackers:
            target_id, _ = attackers[0]
            target = execution_engine.current_members[target_id]
            execution_engine.attack(me, target)
        else:
            # Reinforce top alliances
            if benefactors:
                top_ally_id, _ = benefactors[0]
                top_ally = execution_engine.current_members[top_ally_id]
                execution_engine.offer(me, top_ally, True)

def agent_action(execution_engine, member_id):
    me = execution_engine.current_members[member_id]
    attack_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict['victim']
    attacks_against_me = attack_matrix[me.id]

    # Find attackers excluding self
    attacker_ids = [i for i, attacks in enumerate(attacks_against_me) if attacks > 0 and i != me.id]

    if me.vitality < 50.0 and me.cargo > 10.0:
        # Offer help to the member with the highest benefit given to me
        benefit_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict['benefit']
        benefits_received = benefit_matrix[:, me.id]
        if benefits_received.sum() > 0:
            best_benefactor = benefits_received.argmax()
            target = execution_engine.current_members[best_benefactor]
            execution_engine.offer(me, target, True)
    elif attacker_ids:
        # Attack the member who has attacked me the most
        top_attacker_id = attacker_ids[0]
        max_attacks = attacks_against_me[top_attacker_id]
        for attacker_id in attacker_ids:
            if attacks_against_me[attacker_id] > max_attacks:
                top_attacker_id = attacker_id
                max_attacks = attacks_against_me[attacker_id]
        target = execution_engine.current_members[top_attacker_id]
        execution_engine.attack(me, target)
    else:
        # If no attackers, collaborate with the most beneficial member
        benefit_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict['benefit']
        benefits_given = benefit_matrix[me.id]
        if benefits_given.sum() > 0:
            best_partner_id = benefits_given.argmax()
            partner = execution_engine.current_members[best_partner_id]
            execution_engine.bear(me, partner)
        else:
            # Default action: offer to a random member
            for member in execution_engine.current_members.values():
                if member.id != me.id:
                    execution_engine.offer(me, member, True)
                    break

    benefit_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict['benefit']

    # Calculate how many times I have been attacked
    attacks_against_me = victim_matrix[me.id].sum()

    if attacks_against_me > 50:
        # If heavily attacked, seek alliances
        # Find the member who benefits me the most
        benefit_from_members = benefit_matrix[:, me.id]
        target_id = benefit_from_members.argmax()
        target = execution_engine.current_members[target_id]
        execution_engine.offer(me, target, True)
    else:
        # Attack the member who has attacked others the most
        total_attacks_by_members = victim_matrix.sum(axis=0)
        total_attacks_by_members[member_id] = 0  # Exclude self
        target_id = total_attacks_by_members.argmax()
        target = execution_engine.current_members[target_id]
        execution_engine.attack(me, target)
